    {
      "id": "guide_onboarding",
      "title": "🚀 Onboarding Guide — Set Up Mission Control",
      "description": "Welcome to Mission Control! Follow these steps to complete your setup. Work through each subtask in order.\n\n**Tip:** Click on a subtask to see detailed instructions. Check it off when done.",
      "status": "permanent",
      "project": "guides",
      "tags": [
        "guide",
        "setup"
      ],
      "subtasks": [
        {
          "id": "sub_001",
          "title": "1. Enable GitHub Pages: Settings → Pages → Branch: main → Save",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_002",
          "title": "2. Create GitHub Token: github.com/settings/tokens → Generate (classic) → Scope: repo",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_003",
          "title": "3. Connect Dashboard: Open your GitHub Pages URL → Click 'Connect GitHub' → Paste token",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_004",
          "title": "4. Install Tailscale: brew install tailscale && tailscale up",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_005",
          "title": "5. Enable Funnel: tailscale funnel 18789 → Copy your URL",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_006",
          "title": "6. Generate Webhook Token: openssl rand -hex 32 → Save it",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_007",
          "title": "7. Add GitHub Webhook: Settings → Webhooks → Add → URL: https://YOUR-TAILSCALE-URL/hooks/github?token=YOUR-TOKEN",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_008",
          "title": "8. Test: Create a task, move to In Progress, verify MoltBot receives notification",
          "done": false
        }
      ],
      "priority": "high",
      "comments": [
        {
          "author": "Mission Control",
          "text": "Once all steps are complete, you can archive this guide or keep it as reference. Your setup is done when MoltBot responds to task changes!",
          "timestamp": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z"
        }
      ],
      "createdAt": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "guide_user",
      "title": "📖 User Guide — How to Use Mission Control",
      "description": "Learn how to use Mission Control effectively. Both you AND MoltBot can manage tasks!\n\n**Two ways to manage tasks:**\n• 👤 **You** — Use the Dashboard UI (drag & drop, buttons, forms)\n• 🤖 **MoltBot** — Uses CLI scripts or edits tasks.json directly",
      "status": "permanent",
      "project": "guides",
      "tags": [
        "guide",
        "help"
      ],
      "subtasks": [
        {
          "id": "sub_001",
          "title": "— THE BOARD —",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_002",
          "title": "Columns: Permanent (recurring) → Backlog → In Progress → Review → Done",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_003",
          "title": "Drag & Drop: Move tasks between columns to change status",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_004",
          "title": "Click task card to open details and edit",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_005",
          "title": "— CREATING TASKS —",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_006",
          "title": "👤 You: Click '+' button in any column header",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_007",
          "title": "🤖 MoltBot: Edits data/tasks.json or uses CLI",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_008",
          "title": "— TASK DETAILS —",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_009",
          "title": "Title: Short, clear name for the task",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_010",
          "title": "Description: Detailed instructions (Markdown supported)",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_011",
          "title": "Subtasks: Break work into smaller steps (checkable)",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_012",
          "title": "Comments: Add notes, feedback, or progress updates",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_013",
          "title": "Priority: High (🔴) / Medium (🟡) / Low (🟢)",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_014",
          "title": "Project: Organize tasks by project/category",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_015",
          "title": "— WORKFLOW WITH MOLTBOT —",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_016",
          "title": "1. Create task in Backlog with clear description",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_017",
          "title": "2. Move to 'In Progress' → MoltBot gets notified via webhook",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_018",
          "title": "3. MoltBot works on task, updates subtasks & adds comments",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_019",
          "title": "4. MoltBot moves to 'Review' when done",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_020",
          "title": "5. You review: Approve → Done, or add feedback → back to In Progress",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_021",
          "title": "— DASHBOARD FEATURES —",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_022",
          "title": "🔍 Search: Filter tasks by text",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_023",
          "title": "📁 Project filter: Click project buttons to filter",
          "done": false
        },
        {
          "id": "sub_024",
          "title": "⚙️ Settings: Add/edit projects",
